r268 | fabrice.colin@gmail.com | 2014-05-19 21:30:32 +0200 (Mon, 19 May 2014) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/sample-emails/attachments.xml
   M /trunk/src/CampaignSQL.cc
   M /trunk/src/CampaignSQL.h
   M /trunk/src/ConfigurationFile.cc
   M /trunk/src/ConfigurationFile.h
   M /trunk/src/DBUsageLogger.cc
