------------------------------------------------------------------------
r249 | fabrice.colin@gmail.com | 2011-11-23 04:37:43 +0100 (Wed, 23 Nov 2011) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/LibETPANProvider.cc

Backtracked on SVN r222. By definition, MIME encoded-word requires that spaces
be replaced with underscores, and that underscores be encoded. In addition,
question marks and equal signs have to be encoded too.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r248 | fabrice.colin@gmail.com | 2011-10-24 10:51:47 +0200 (Mon, 24 Oct 2011) | 3 lines
