r217 | fabrice.colin | 2010-06-24 13:55:26 +0200 (Thu, 24 Jun 2010) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.cc

In SMTPSession::setServer() compare the domain name, current host name and its
address with the configured mail relay which may be any of these, to determine
which port to connect to.

