------------------------------------------------------------------------
r164 | fabrice.colin | 2009-11-12 14:03:29 +0100 (Thu, 12 Nov 2009) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/LibESMTPProvider.cc
   M /trunk/src/LibESMTPProvider.h
   M /trunk/src/LibETPANProvider.cc
   M /trunk/src/LibETPANProvider.h
   M /trunk/src/MessageDetails.cc
   M /trunk/src/MessageDetails.h
