   M /trunk/src/SMTPProvider.h
   M /trunk/src/Substitute.cc
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemail.cc

Subject, From, Reply-To, Sender and Resent-From are substituted on the fly.
Substitute doesn't need to be told to look for custom fields, it does so
automatically and isn't restricted to just 6.
SMTPMessage::buildHeaders() builds common headers to both providers.

