   M /trunk/src/givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemaild.cc

The slave exits with status code 10 when hitting error SMTP_ERR_INVAL, which
the daemon identifies as an explicit request for a restart.
Better let the daemon set campaigns status to Sent, once all slaves are done.

