------------------------------------------------------------------------
r46 | fabrice.colin | 2009-05-15 13:05:28 +0200 (Fri, 15 May 2009) | 9 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.cc
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.h

Fixed resource priorities mismatch.
A MX ResourceRecord could actually be an IP address if the fallback-to-A-record
was triggered.
Record an error type SMTP_ERR_DROPPED_CONNECTION if we are disconnected right
after connection.
In generateMessages(), message objects were not deleted on failure.
A failure of smtp_start_session() should cause dispatchMessages() to return
false so that all recipients are marked as failed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r45 | fabrice.colin | 2009-05-15 12:55:56 +0200 (Fri, 15 May 2009) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/Resolver.cc

Fixed priorities mismatch. Skip resource "dev.null".

------------------------------------------------------------------------
