------------------------------------------------------------------------
r35 | fabrice.colin | 2009-04-20 14:02:24 +0200 (Mon, 20 Apr 2009) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc

Better use readdir64().

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r34 | fabrice.colin | 2009-04-18 06:51:17 +0200 (Sat, 18 Apr 2009) | 8 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.1
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemail.1

Extensive changes to csv2givemail to run in process mode. All of it is
abstracted by the RunUnits class. Previously, each row (ie campaign) was
processed sequentially and domains were handled by separate threads. Now, up
to maxslaves campaigns are processed in parallel.
There's support for a timestamp column that could be used for instance for a
bill date when emailing invoices.
Updated manual pages.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
