------------------------------------------------------------------------
r31 | fabrice.colin | 2009-04-15 15:44:43 +0200 (Wed, 15 Apr 2009) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.cc
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.h
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemail.cc

Moved sendEmails to SMTPSession::generateMessages(), extended it to check if
the message is to be personalized for each recipient. If it isn't, generate
just one SMTPMessage for all recipients on the given domain.
Some minor changes to dumMessage().

