   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.cc
   M /trunk/src/SMTPSession.h

If initilizeAddresses(), initializeTopQueue(), cycleServers() or createSession()
fail, propagate the error so that the message is logged as failed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r12 | fabrice.colin | 2009-03-29 10:09:14 +0200 (Sun, 29 Mar 2009) | 3 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/DBStatusUpdater.cc
   M /trunk/src/DBStatusUpdater.h
   M /trunk/src/StatusUpdater.cc
   M /trunk/src/StatusUpdater.h
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemail.cc

StatusUpdater::updateRecipientsStatus() updates the status of all recipients
belonging to a given domain name, domain name that has no MX record.

