------------------------------------------------------------------------
r8 | fabrice.colin | 2009-03-29 08:44:16 +0200 (Sun, 29 Mar 2009) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/ConfigurationFile.cc
   M /trunk/src/ConfigurationFile.h
   M /trunk/src/csv2givemail.cc
   M /trunk/src/givemail.cc

ConfigurationFile::findDomainLimits() indicates whether a domain has MX records
and is "usable". Those that don't are now skipped by givemail, while
csv2givemail continues defaulting to using the domain name as pseudo MX record.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
